Revision history for Perl extension Sys::Signals::Block.

{{$NEXT}}

0.11  2018-06-03
    - Add object oriented interface, where signal names can be passed to new()
      instead of on the import line.
    - Kwalitee: Add META.json.
    - Switch bug tracker to github issues.
    - Use Dist::Zilla to build the dist.
    - Make signature test an author test.
    - Use Moo internally, drop Class::Accessor dependency
    - Move compile test to the front of the test suite
    - Add sanity test to make sure signal delivery works on the current platform

0.10  Fri Nov 13 2009
    - disable signature test unless TEST_SIGNATURE is enabled, otherwise test
      fails if keyserver is unreachable.

0.03  Mon Oct 26 2009
    - fix "bareword" errors in signals.t
    - add SIGNATURE checking test

0.02  Mon Oct 26 2009
    - Makefile.PL check that POSIX->SigSet is supported on this platform

0.01  Sun Oct 25 2009
    - original version
